commit 33bb108bd8c053de4ce37c6db26dd32ea20f46e2
Author: Tor Lillqvist <tml@iki.fi>
Date:   Thu Sep 10 18:49:31 2009 +0300

    Revert "[basic-win32] Increase performance of Uniscribe code"

